Hi I’m Bunny!
Welcome to our Garden！
Incase you get stuck during the game, click on me for instructions.
We grow plants to breathe fresh air and grow our food. Let me show you how to use the tools.
Click on this Blue Watering Pot to water your plant every day.
Click on this Food icon to give plant nutrition so that plant grows healthy.
Click on this Bug Spray to kill all the insects.
Click on this Scissors to cut small weed around your plant.
The drops over the watering pot shows the amount of water needed for the plant. Once full, come back the next day to water the plant.
This shows the health of the plant. If you take care of your plants regularly, you’ll get a surprise!
Click on your plant to learn new fun facts about it!
We grow plants to breathe fresh air and grow our food. Let me show you how to use the tools.
The progress bar shows the current growing stage of your plant.
